  "bio_raw": "Past placement experiences of teaching overseas had given me the opportunity to teach a wide variety of students from different nationalities, backgrounds, age groups and abilities. My internship report catered towards planning, executing, reflecting and receiving feedback on a real teaching episode founded on current educational research, theories and methodologies. Currently, I am teaching English Literature at the Department of English and Humanities at University of Liberal Arts.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Teaching approaches, Educational research and theories, Psychology, and Literary Studies"
  ],
